sentences: Daisuke Kawai (川合大介 / だいすけ・かわい) was born December 16, 1976 in Tokyo, Japan.

Daisuke "KM-MARKIT" Kawai was born in Tokyo, Japan on December 16, 1976.
In 1998, he joined the Urbarian Gym, a hip-hop group who was created by Japanese rapper ZEEBRA in 1997.
